These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-1::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: september, july, january, june, may, august
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: daffodil, amaryllis, iris, orchid, begonia, zinnia
 1. the person who's birthday is in january is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##5
 3. the person who's birthday is in may is not the person who growsbegonia##6
 4. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##5
 5. the person who growsbegonia is somewhere to the left of the person who growsiris##5
 6. the person who growsamaryllis is somewhere to the right of the person who growsiris##5
 7. the person who growsbegonia is not the person who's birthday is in july##6
 8. the person who growszinnia is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere between the person who growszinnia and the person who's birthday is in june##7
10. the person who growsiris is on the left or right of the person who growsorchid##3
11. the person who growszinnia is somewhere to the right of the person who growsdaffodil##5
12. the person who growszinnia is somewhere to the left of the person who growsorchid##5
13. the person who growsdaffodil is the person who's birthday is in september##1
14. the person who growsiris is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5
15. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who growsorchid##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |   3    |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Birthday   | june   | september | january   | august     | july    | may   |
| Flower           | begonia | daffodil   | zinnia | orchid | iris | amaryllis |

