.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-2::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, mirinda, fanta, water, tea
6 different games are played: monopoly, whist, snooker, bridge, domino, poker
 1. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
 2. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 3. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 4. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
 5. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person playing domino##1
 6. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 7. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the person drinking mirinda##5
 8. the person drinking coffee is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person drinking water is not the person playing domino##6
10. the person playing monopoly is somewhere between the person playing poker and the person playing bridge##7
11. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
12. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person playing whist##1
13. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
14. the person playing poker is in an even position##4
15. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person playing bridge##5
16. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
17. the person drinking fanta is somewhere between the person playing whist and the person drinking water##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |     5      |    6     |
| Beverage   | cola | tea | fanta | water     | mirinda      | coffee |
| Game           | whist         | snooker        | domino   | bridge | monopoly | poker    |

