.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-3::.
There 6 different types of food: spinach, radish, onion, pear, blueberry, asparagus
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, ritmeester, montecristo, chaman, oliveros, old-henry
 1. the person eating onion is on the left of the person eating radish##1
 2. the person eating spinach is in an even position##4
 3. the chaman-smoker is somewhere to the left of the davidoff-smoker##5
 4. the ritmeester-smoker is not the person eating pear##6
 5. the person eating spinach is not the davidoff-smoker##6
 6. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
 7. the ritmeester-smoker is on the far left##1
 8. the person eating blueberry is somewhere to the left of the person eating asparagus##5
 9. the davidoff-smoker is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3
10. the oliveros-smoker is somewhere between the person eating blueberry and the person eating radish##7
11. the old-henry-smoker is in an odd position##4
12. the davidoff-smoker is on the left or right of the person eating spinach##3
13. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the left of the davidoff-smoker##5
14. the person eating pear is somewhere to the left of the old-henry-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |    5     |       6       |
| Food   | blueberry        | pear | asparagus    | spinach    | onion | radish |
| Cigar      | ritmeester | oliveros  | old-henry | chaman | davidoff | montecristo      |

