.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-4::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: skateboard, tram, trike, ship, bus, snowmobile
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: december, october, august, april, september, may
 1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bus##5
 4. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in october is not the person driving the bus##6
 6. the person driving the trike is somewhere between the person driving the snowmobile and the person driving the bus##7
 7. the person driving the trike is somewhere between the person driving the skateboard and the person driving the snowmobile##7
 8. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere between the person driving the trike and the person driving the ship##7
10. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
11. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
12. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##5
13. the person who's birthday is in august is the person driving the ship##1
14. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the left of the person driving the skateboard##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |   3   |       4       |    5    |   6   |
| Transport      | ship | tram | snowmobile | trike | bus | skateboard   |
| Birthday   | august  | april      | december | september     | may | october |

