 1. the person traveling to miami is somewhere to the right of the videographer##5
 2. the person traveling to london is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to miami##5
 3. the mechanic is on the right of the dressmaker##1
 4. the lawyer is on the far left##1
 5. the security-guard is between the person traveling to boston and the videographer##2
 6. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the videographer is somewhere to the left of the mechanic##5
 8. the videographer is somewhere between the musician and the lawyer##7
 9. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3
10. the person traveling to london is on the far right##1
11. the person traveling to boston is the dressmaker##1
12. the person traveling to new-york is not the dressmaker##6
13. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
14. the person traveling to new-york is the person traveling to new-york##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |  3   |     4     |     5      |   6    |
| Job   | lawyer | videographer | security-guard  | dressmaker | mechanic | musician |
| City           | hamburg  | colone  | miami | boston  | new-york     | london    |

