 2. the person watching scientific movies is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 3. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
 4. the owner of the pony is somewhere between the owner of the frog and the person watching family movies##7
 5. the owner of the hamster is somewhere between the owner of the fish and the owner of the pony##7
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the right of the owner of the frog##5
 7. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
 8. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the fish##5
10. the person watching zombie movies is in an even position##4
11. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
12. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the right of the person watching zombie movies##5
13. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3     |     4      |       5       |    6     |
| Pet   | fish | hamster | frog   | pony  | guinea-pig      | hedgehog  |
| Movie-Genre         | comedy      | zombie | thriller | horror | family | scientific |

