.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-19::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: january, july, february, april, october, march
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: comedy, spy, western, martial-arts, zombie, fantasy
 1. the person watching western movies is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in january is in an odd position##4
 3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
 5. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the person watching western movies##5
 6. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person watching comedy movies##2
 7. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching spy movies##5
 8. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is in an odd position##4
10. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the right of the person watching fantasy movies##5
11. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
12. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in february and the person watching spy movies##7
13. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##5

.:: Answer ::.
