.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-20::.
6 different pets are kept: ferret, horse, turtle, lizard, hamster, rat
There are 6 different favourite colors: azure, chestnut, blood-red, grey, yellow, green
 1. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
 2. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
 3. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the right of the person who likes blood-red##5
 4. the owner of the ferret is somewhere between the person who likes grey and the person who likes chestnut##7
 5. the person who likes green is on the left or right of the person who likes blood-red##3
 6. the owner of the turtle is the person who likes yellow##1
 7. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the right of the person who likes grey##5
 8. the person who likes yellow is somewhere to the left of the owner of the ferret##5
 9. the person who likes yellow is somewhere to the left of the person who likes blood-red##5
10. the person who likes chestnut is somewhere to the right of the person who likes green##5
11. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
12. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the right of the person who likes grey##5
13. the owner of the horse is somewhere between the owner of the ferret and the owner of the turtle##7
14. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
15. the person who likes yellow is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |        1        |      2      |     3      |     4     |      5      |     6      |
| Pet   | turtle         | lizard | horse | ferret   | rat | hamster  |
| Color     | yellow | grey  | blood-red  | green | chestnut  | azure |

 